column2: Text mining: extracting useful information from text
column7: Natural language processing, parsing free form text
column8: Provenance annotation: you can use metadata to keep track of where results came from
column9: Semantic integration, mashups - you can write tools to discover, collect and integrate online data
column10: Taxonomic name resolution: you can use and adapt tools to map one set of names to another
column11: Documentation: you can make screencasts and write clear how-to documents
column12: Web service interfaces - you can design and implement interfaces to wrap existing tools
column13: Workflows: you can assemble web services (or other resources) into an executable workflow
column14: Visualization: you can adapt an existing visualization tool for new inputs and capabilities
column15: Processing structured data (XML, JSON, YAML, etc...)
column16: Something else - you can contribute to this project in ways we haven't imagined yet
